data.description: This is a beautiful two family house ready to be moved into.  The property has two houses on it.  The main house has 3 bedrooms with a living room, dinning room, and family room. It also has a full finished walk out basement that can be used as a mother in law apartment. Basement is fully finished with kitchen and bathroom.  The second house has a 1 bedroom with eat in kitchen and living room.  The property is 50x100 and taxes are an amazing $3900.  The backyard is very large with an inground pool.  Property is conveinently located close to all transportation and shopping.  No Brokers please, agent home.
data.whatILove: Extra Large yard with inground pool and access to full walkout basement with complete kitchen for entertaining. Also, the second house is the tenant's apartment and is completely detached from the owner.  Provides privacy, and conveniently located close to all transportation and shopping.
